high_descs: Turn right, go to table across room.
Pick up knife off of table, in front of tomato and pump dispenser.
Turn around, go to table across room.
Slice tomato on table, below the right loaf of bread.
Turn around, go to table across room.
Place knife on table, in front of shaker and to left and above potato.
Turn around, go to table across room.
Pick up end slice of cut tomato off of table.
Turn left, go across room to stove.
Put tomato slice in pan on right back burner of stove.
Pick up pan from back right burner of stove.
Turn around, proceed across room.  Turn left, face table table.
Place pan with tomato slice on table, below the two loaves of bread.
anns.task_desc: Move shaker to a different table, cut a tomato with a knife, move knife to pan on stove, move pan and tomato to table.

high_descs: Turn right and go to the front of the white table.
Pick up the yellow knife in front of the liquid soap.
Turn around and go to the small round black table in the corner.
Slice the red tomato on the table.
Turn around and go back to the white table.
Place the yellow knife on the table in front of the bread and salt shaker.
Turn around and go back to the black round table with the sliced tomato.
Pick up one slice of tomato from the table.
Turn left and go to the stove.
Place the tomato slice in the brown pan on the right back burner.
Pick up the pan with the tomato slice in it.
Turn around and go back to the black round table.
Place the pan with tomato in it on the table on the right side in front of the bread..
anns.task_desc: Move the pan on the stove with a slice of tomato in it to the table.

high_descs: Move forward towards the door, then head right to stand at the white table.
Pick up the sharp knife from the table.
Turn around and carry the knife to the round black table.
Use the knife to slice the tomato on the table.
Turn around again and carry the knife to the white table.
Place the knife on the table in front of the salt shaker.
Turn back around and return to the black table with the tomato.
Pick up a slice of tomato from the table.
Turn left and carry the tomato slice across the kitchen to the stove.
Place the tomato slice in the pan on the back right burner of the stove.
Pick up the pan and tomato from the stove.
Turn around and carry the pan and tomato slice across the kitchen to the black round table on your left.
Place the pan with the tomato slice on the table.
anns.task_desc: Move a pan beneath a tomato slice on the black table.
